summary: All the sketches for the 30 top tier rewards of my book are done!! Whoo that was a lot of Dan and Phil @_@  The Phan Sketchbook...
caption:
All the sketches for the 30 top tier rewards of my book are done!! Whoo that was a lot of Dan and Phil @_@ 

The Phan Sketchbook is now 114% backed on Kickstarter, which is AMAZING!! The campaign ends October 11th, so you still have 7 days to support the book! Here is a link to the project: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/262278830/phan-sketchbook. 

After Oct 11, I’ll have the books made (250 copies), and will be putting it up on my Tictail shop for future sales :) Thank you to everyone who has supported me so far!
